istopher Daniel Barnes 配音）渡完蜜月，开始她在皇宫中身为王妃的生活，一开始实在无法适应这样的新生活，但她努力的去适应这种全新的生活。另一方面，辛德瑞拉那群“小朋友”也很想念她，由于辛德瑞拉实在太忙了，没空跟大家玩在一起，吉安帕（Rob Paulsen 配音）甚至还去求神仙教母把他变成人类，他认为如此一来也许辛德瑞拉就会花较多的时间来陪陪他！最后无论是辛德瑞拉还是她的朋友，都发现即使最美好的梦想成真，一切都还是要保持真实的自我，这才是最快乐的生活！","date":"2002-02-26","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/05/e7/112884_klK3L.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/05/e7/112884_klK3L.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/05/e7/112884_klK3L.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/05/e7/112884_klK3L.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/05/e7/112884_klK3L.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":0,"total":32,"score":6.2,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":6,"6":14,"7":9,"8":2,"9":0,"10":0}},"tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":15},{"name":"欧美","count":15},{"name":"迪士尼","count":9},{"name":"Disney","count":9},{"name":"2002","count":9},{"name":"动画电影","count":4},{"name":"童年","count":3},{"name":"灰姑娘","count":2},{"name":"童话","count":2},{"name":"小说","count":1},{"name":"其他","count":1}],"eps":1,"collection":{"wish":6,"collect":78,"doing":3,"on_hold":2,"dropped":7}},{"id":4840,"type":2,"name":"一騎当千 Dragon Destiny","name_cn":"一骑当千 Dragon Destiny","summary":"本作以讲述成都学园的生活开篇，刘·关·张为主要表现对象。天下大势虽继承于第一部，但涉及到吕布、董卓、左慈等人的情节有所变更。另外，与马谡对决败北的郭嘉于DD中死亡。\r\n真·第一女主角=孙策于第三话末尾登场。","date":"2007-02-26","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/74/24/4840_LDMN3.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/74/24/4840_LDMN3.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/74/24/4840_LDMN3.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/74/24/4840_LDMN3.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/74/24/4840_LDMN3.jpg"},"rating":{"rank":6968,"total":650,"score":6.1,"count":{"1":2,"2":5,"3":7,"4":26,"5":104,"6":293,"7":157,"8":38,"9":9,"10":9}},"tags":[{"name":"肉","count":124},{"name":"TV","count":89},{"name":"百合","count":82},{"name":"2007","count":82},{"name":"肉番","count":64},{"name":"一骑当千DD","count":61},{"name":"爆衣","count":48},{"name":"卖肉","